{"tid":2003842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會員#176452 普巴踢法似我屈完人影裙底，事後柒左仲唔肯道歉","createTime":"2020-05-06T05:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:24:44.000Z","uid":3358,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dcfa9c6a35be97c96993f593295930cfa725e8","tid":2003842,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"事源<br />\n<br />\n美孚C出口電梯有百老匯員工影裙底（有圖）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隻49000一黎就放左當事人大頭相上黎看圖作文，屈鳩人偷影裙底，但完全無實質證據<br />\n<br />\n然後#145當事人上水話上司見到個post要佢解決件事<br />\n<br />\n而呢位被屈既巴打仲向隻49000道歉想解決件事<br />\n<br />\n但隻49000柒左又唔撚認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQ8QFWX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQ8QFWX.png&h=a7bd9f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾你屈個個都道歉你條柒頭仲唔肯為屈人而道歉？<br />\n你係唔係男人黎？"},{"pid":"40f8bb70f442c5b07e583f45fa7d8af6309d0954","tid":2003842,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"推到49000道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a980bd0f49329d84f3457a74699d61780d57d1b","tid":2003842,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"57bd162b4526d625e97d487c986f37960ad935de","tid":2003842,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"好明顯<br />\n當事人比該post樓主恐嚇<br />\n所以先會道歉，但明明係受害者<br />\n比人恰到上心口<br />\n理由只得一個<br />\n當事人已經受到威脅"},{"pid":"8b8f615f68d40228ab977a05572d0b5654c21b30","tid":2003842,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57bd162b4526d625e97d487c986f37960ad935de","tid":2003842,"uid":71508,"like":0,"d